The main.css file:


.one {
    position: absolute; width: 250px; height: 80px;
    top: 10px; left: 80px;
    background-color: #c0c0c0;
}
.two {
   position: absolute; width: 250px; height: 80px;
    top: 10px; left: 350px;
    background-color: #ff00ff; 
}
.three {
   position: fixed; width: 520px; height:200px;
    top: 100px; left: 80px; z-index: -1;
    background-color: #00ff00; 

}

The main web page with main.css attached:

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <title>CSS Positioning Application</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="main.css">
    </head
    <body>
       <div class="one">
            <p>This is section one. The place for the website menu.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="two">
            <p>This is section one. The place for the website introduction.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="three">
            <p>This is section three. The place for the website contact</p>

        </div>
    </body>


</html>
